    question: "You join a project with no test documentation, no test cases, and no test strategy. Where do you start?",
    hint: "Assess the current state, gather knowledge from stakeholders, create a test strategy, document existing functionality via exploratory testing, and build a backlog of test cases starting from the most critical areas.",
